INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1334200, 'Mülltrennungssimulator 2021', 'The Mülltrennungssimulator 2021 is a revolutionary mix of game genres. For this idle game, a quick grasp and a small dose of skill is essential. Because when the state decided to pay premiums for good waste separation, you sensed the chance and bought a landfill. The faster you sort the garbage into the correct bin, the more money you make!<br />
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1334230, 'Revolution: The Spark', '<img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334230/extras/Shooting_scene.gif?t=1648167093" /><br>Fight back in Revolution: The Spark, a story-driven, turn-based tactical RPG. With dwindling resources and enemies at every turn, what will you do to survive this revolution?<br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334230/extras/Ayiric2.png?t=1648167093" /><h2 class="bb_tag">The Story</h2>On the brink of revolt, the common people cry out for justice from their heartless queen. This story is set in an alternate steampunk world in the early 20th century in the Capital of the strongest Empire in the world. The game tells a story of a military veteran, Alex, who becomes increasingly frustrated with the growing corruption of the monarchy and the exploitation of the common folk. When Alex''s brother gets arrested for an attempted coup, Alex will have no choice but to fight if he ever wants to see his brother again. It appears that a concentration of power lies in the hands of a powerful few. But there is more to this than meets the eye. These few are being manipulated by supernatural beings that feed off of the fervor, lust, and wrath of humankind. <strong>A spark</strong> of revolution will change it all.<br>  <br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334230/extras/Ayiric2.png?t=1648167093" /><h2 class="bb_tag">CORE FEATURES</h2><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Strategic Turn-based Combat – People are your greatest assets, so take care of them. Those who fall in combat will need time to recover.<br><br></li><li>Recruit up to 25 Allies across 7 distinct Classes – You’ll need all the help that you can find on your journey to unseat the Empress. But beware, as some of your companions might not like others.<br><br></li><li>Explore 9 Dynamic Locations – From the mines to the noble villas, you must fight your way to the steps of the Empress’ palace itself across 9 exciting, beautiful, hand-drawn, isometric locations.<br><br></li><li>Forge Your Own Path – Your actions shape the future of a corrupt Empire. Choose how you want to solve conflict. Will you conquer all or reason with your foes? Every decision you make in travel, conversation, and combat has a meaningful effect on the outcome as your story unfolds.<br><br></li><li>Discover secrets and Unlock 5 Different Endings. – Explore and talk to everyone. You never know what you might find. There are many routes and options that will help you steer the ultimate fate of the Empire.<br><br></li><li>Steampunk Victorian Culture – Master the weapons of the early 20th century in this steam-fueled alternate reality where things aren’t what they seem.<br><br></li><li>Decide what you fight for – Peace? A new world order? Or do you just want power for yourself? Everything is possible in Revolution: The Spark.</li></ul>', 0, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334230/header.jpg?t=1648167093', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1334280, 'Elaborate Lands', 'Elaborate Lands is a relaxing, turn-based strategy game focused on district building, adjacency effects and economy management.<br><br><strong>What Elaborate Lands offers:</strong><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Turn-based gameplay with immediate turns<br></li><li>Challenging building placement &amp; adjacency effects<br></li><li>Goods production and resource management<br></li><li>Population demands (food, faith and amenities)<br></li><li>Over 50 goods, buildings and technologies<br></li><li>Different randomly generated maps and various biomes<br></li><li>Random events<br></li><li>Optional Military</li></ul><br><strong>What Elaborate Lands doesn’t offer:</strong><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Real-time gameplay or simulation<br></li><li>Multiplayer<br></li><li>AI Opponents<br></li><li>Transportation and logistics</li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>ADDICTIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2> The core game systems offer variety and depth in all game phases:<br><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li><strong>Early Game</strong>: Found your first settlements and construct buildings to gather resources and build houses to increase your workforce. Establish farms to gather food and feed your population.<br></li><li><strong>Midgame</strong>: Research technologies to unlock higher-tier buildings and goods. Supply demands for faith and amenities. Expand your territory and gather advanced materials to construct public buildings in your towns.<br></li><li><strong>Lategame</strong>: Optimize your settlements and increase your profits by constructing improvement buildings.<br></li><li><strong>Endgame</strong>: Build epic monuments to stand the test of time.</li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>ENJOY AT YOUR OWN PACE</strong></h2>In Elaborate Lands, turns are immediate and most buildings are instantly constructed, but resources are only gathered once and are therefore somewhat limited. This rewards <strong>strategic decision making</strong>, while you can enjoy the game at your own pace. Elaborate Lands avoids both the stress of real-time strategy games and the lategame slog of other turn-based strategy games with their increasingly longer turns.<h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>DEEP BUILDING SYSTEMS</strong></h2><br>Elaborate Lands takes district building &amp; adjacency effects to the next level.<br><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Use clever <strong>combinations of terrain features and buildings</strong>: Nearby trees increase the effectiveness of Wood Cutters, while Sawmills double the Wood production within its influence radius. To tap the full potential, build a Stockpile to further improve all nearby construction material production buildings.</li></ul><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Make use of the different <strong>building mechanics</strong>:<br> ◦ Churches gain Faith from the total population within a <strong>certain radius</strong>.<br> ◦ Castles gain Influence from all buildings that have an <strong>uninterrupted connection</strong> to it.<br> ◦ Farms consist of <strong>multiple tiles</strong> that can be manually placed and require careful planning.<br> ◦ Overlapping Trading Posts can form a <strong>network</strong>. The more you have in your network, the more coins you can gather.</li></ul><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>The <strong>terrain system</strong> of Elaborate Lands has 4 different levels of terrain fertility and 2 different levels of terrain elevation, which affect the yield of farm tiles. You will need to optimize the shape and size of your farms to optimize your resource output.</li></ul><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>As the buildable area within regions is limited, <strong>specializing your settlements</strong> will be advantageous: Several farming villages are necessary to meet the food demands of a densely populated city. Plan carefully where to construct which type of settlement. </li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>CHALLENGING GOODS PRODUCTION</strong></h2>Elaborate Lands uses a familiar, yet <strong>unique mechanic</strong> for the production of goods: Goods are produced at fixed ratios between inputs and outputs. Complete all inputs of a group to unlock its output. You will need to place your buildings carefully to unlock as many groups as possible.<br><br>The variety of goods offer depth to the game, as their variable availability on different maps demand new strategies each time.<h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>RANDOM MAPS &amp; BIOMES</strong></h2>Elaborate Lands has randomly generated maps and several unique biomes that offer unique challenges and endless replayability: Fertile land in the Desert is limited to nearby rivers and oases. The Northern Taiga offers an abundance of forests, but limited farmland.<h2 class="bb_tag"><strong>OPTIONAL MILITARY</strong></h2>While military conquest of some regions will be possible (during/after Early Access), combat is optional and not the main focus of the game. There are no AI opponents that compete with you or threaten your accomplishments.<br><br><br><i>This game has been funded by <strong>FFF Bayern</strong> and <strong>Bundesministerium für Verkehr und digitale Infrastruktur</strong> (BMVI) of the Federal Republic of Germany.</i>', 0, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334280/header.jpg?t=1646223516', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1334360, 'Out of Control', '<img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/extras/tape-demo.png?t=1593101002" /><br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://healthpotionstudios.itch.io/out-of-control-demo1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"  ><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/extras/itch-download.png?t=1593101002" /></a><br><br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/extras/tape-description.png?t=1593101002" /><br>Out of Control is a platformer where the controls randomize each level!<br>Play through 30+ levels and fight challenging bosses in a game that makes you say ''Which one is jump again?''<br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/extras/tape-features.png?t=1593101002" /><br><ul class="bb_ul"><li>Hand drawn art<br></li><li>Frustrating but satisfying gameplay<br></li><li>More than 40 levels each with a collectible<br></li><li>Secret exits<br></li><li>More than 20 unique enemy types<br></li><li>Challenging bosses to test your skills</li></ul><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/extras/tape-story.png?t=1593101002" /><br>Professor Croak never intended to cause problems, but coding isn’t easy when you only have three fingers. He wanted to create robots to protect the forest, but instead they malfunctioned and are on a rampage. Armed with the professor’s newest creation, it’s up to Roscoe to stop the robots and bring back peace to the forest.', 0, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334360/header.jpg?t=1593101002', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1334470, 'Mythic Archive', 'The Mythic Archive is a Digital Toolset that lets you prepare and store massive amounts of content for TTRPGs. Prepare handouts, adventure modules, fully automated roleplaying systems, and much more (See list below). <br><br>A list of things you can create with Mythic Archive<br><ul class="bb_ul"><li> Character Sheets<br></li><li> Handouts<br></li><li> Loot tables / Rollable Tables<br></li><li> Automated Dice Rolls <br></li><li> World Maps<br></li><li> Presentations<br></li><li> Combat and Encounters<br></li><li> Items, Status Effects, Skills, and anything imaginable<br></li><li> Character Creation Wizards<br></li><li> Compendiums<br></li><li> Adventure Seeds<br></li><li> Content Packs<br></li><li> Your own Systems<br></li><li> Campaigns, Plotlines and Worldbuilding<br><br>Its a passion project focused on blending writing and TTRPG game mechanics for Gamemasters. The goal of the project is provide a knowledgebase of interactive contents and notes that reduces dead time during play (scouring notes for information, counting dice bonuses, explaining rules). Interactive content ranges from videos, to character sheets and maps (feature list below), and these features grow over time. There is a great deal of focus being put into keeping the feature set lightweight and easy to pick up<br><br>This project is built for those who enjoy writing, or enjoy homebrewing content like new characters, fluff and weapons for your favorite systems.<br><br>The application features a simple scripting language and stat tracking features, as well as options for importing content in bulk. You can share your content on the workshop, connect projects together and search them all in a single search bar, its quite powerful!<br><br>In its current state it features <br></li><li> Organization of large amounts of content<br></li><li> World maps with paths, markers and zones<br></li><li> Article Linking and Rich Text formatting<br></li><li> Article Layout customization, great for character sheets<br></li><li> Stat Tracking / Deep Automation Tools for Tabletop RPGs<br></li><li> Combat/initiative Tracking<br></li><li> Character Creation Tools to speed up character creation<br></li><li> Chat/Dice Rolling mechanics<br></li><li> Workshop Support for sharing Adventure Modules, Additional Content, and Custom Systems</li></ul>', 0, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1334470/header.jpg?t=1638941895', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
